JOHANNESBURG - A man has been killed and four other people have been hurt in a shooting on a farm in Brondal. Paramedics arrived on the scene just after 6am on Monday morning and found that a security guard had succumbed to gunshot wounds. A farmer was found in a critical condition in the kitchen and was airlifted to hospital. The other three people sustained minor injuries. Police are now combing the scene of the attack for evidence. Download the Eyewitness News app to your iOS  or Android  device.